## Tech Decisions Already Made

- Language: TypeScript / Python / Go (reason: ...)
- Database: PostgreSQL (existing infra)
- Auth: OAuth via Auth0 (company standard)
- Deployment: AWS ECS, existing CI/CD pipeline

## Team Conventions

- Sprint length: 2 weeks
- Story point scale: Fibonacci (1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13)
- Definition of Done: unit tests + PR review + deployed to staging

## Constraints

- Must integrate with existing Salesforce CRM
- GDPR compliance required — no PII in logs
- Go-live deadline: Q3 2025

## Out of Scope

- Mobile app (web only for v1)
- Admin portal (separate project)
